{"type":"message","id":"8505fe6b","parentId":"e4c068bb","timestamp":"2026-04-04T16:28:38.033Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户担心如果给一个很重的任务，模型可能会在上下文用完之前没解决问题，然后\"卡死\"。这是一个关于如何处理长任务/大上下文消耗的问题。\n\n我有几种方案可以建议：\n\n1. **任务分解** - 把大任务拆成小步骤，分批执行\n2. **spawn 子代理** - 用 isolated session 来跑长任务\n3. **定期保存进度** - 定期把当前进度写入文件，下次继续\n4. **检查点机制** - 用 cron 或手动保存中间状态\n5. **增大上下文** - 如果可能，配置更大的上下文窗口\n\n让我简洁地回复用户，给出实用建议。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n几个建议：\n\n1. **拆任务** — 把大任务拆成小步骤，我每完成一步就写进文件，下次继续\n2. **用子代理** — spawn 一个 isolated session 跑后台任务，不占用主会话上下文\n3. **进度存档** — 重要任务随时写进度到 `~/self-improving/` 或 workspace，下次能续上\n4. **增大上下文** — 如果你经常跑长任务，可以调大 `models.json` 里的上下文窗口\n\n你目前模型上限是 205k，如果还不够可以试试换上下文更大的模型。你有什么具体任务想跑吗？我帮你规划一下怎么拆分 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":12000,"output":271,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12271,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775320114327,"responseId":"chatcmpl-ddf6d25a-560e-4f6a-b3c5-03c9b1d514dc"}}
{"type":"message","id":"43f2a567","parentId":"8505fe6b","timestamp":"2026-04-04T16:29:19.214Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sun 2026-04-05 00:29 GMT+8] 学习：拆任务 — 把大任务拆成小步骤，我每完成一步就写进文件，下次继续\n用子代理 — spawn 一个 isolated session 跑后台任务，不占用主会话上下文\n进度存档 — 重要任务随时写进度到 ~/self-improving/ 或 workspace，下次能续上"}],"timestamp":1775320159212}}
{"type":"message","id":"3c4eee7a","parentId":"43f2a567","timestamp":"2026-04-04T16:29:26.629Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying they want to \"learn\" or \"study\" these methods - they're acknowledging my suggestions and seems to want me to help them understand or implement these approaches. Let me wait and see if they want more detail, or I can ask what they'd like to do with these methods.\n\nActually, looking at this more - they might just be acknowledging/nodding. Let me keep it brief and see if they want to proceed with something specific.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n明白～ 你想先试试哪个方法？或者有具体的重任务想让我帮你拆分？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":674,"output":114,"cacheRead":11648,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12436,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775320159213,"responseId":"019d5953d061b856bd63a81028e54292"}}
