{"type":"message","id":"8e5e9bda","parentId":"4cadc153","timestamp":"2026-04-04T16:32:29.553Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The skill has been created. Now I should inform the user about this.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n搞定！创建了 `task-weight-estimator` 技能：\n\n- **轻量任务** → 直接执行\n- **中等任务** → 拆步骤 + 进度存档\n- **重量任务** → spawn 子代理\n\n以后你交任务给我，我会自动判断并选最优方式 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":17395,"output":80,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17475,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775320348216,"responseId":"chatcmpl-ee895561-539b-4b83-b5ed-20434317a19a"}}
